        "timestamp": 1715982038
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>If you try to use <code>F = ∅</code>, you'll also run into problems proving <code>⋃₀ F = A</code>.</p>",
        "id": 439295307,
        "sender_full_name": "Richard Osborn",
        "timestamp": 1715982055
